---
title: "US48 — Upload / manage expert content"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ServicesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>PublishService + SendDeliverable
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Deliverable
  A->>B: upload content file / media
  B->>C: attach(content)
  C->>E: Deliverable links the uploaded content
  E-->>C: available
  C-->>B: done
  B-->>A: clients can access it
  note over B,E: scope under review (reconciliation log)
  note over E: files via StorageGateway - rows via SupabaseGateway
